name: utf16-dic-delas-v1
description: The standard Unitex format, for all languages.

name: utf8-dic-delas-v1
description: Valid option for utf16-dic-delas-v1, as standard Unitex format, but only for European languages.

name: utf8-csv-delas-v1
description: Option for utf8-dic-delas-v1 in a open data-interchange context. W3C and FrictionLessData open data format. Equivalent to dic, except by adding a CSV header into the first line of the file.
